			"online":"京东商城:http:\/\/book.360buy.com\/10092246.html 当当网:http:\/\/product.dangdang.com\/product.aspx?product_id=20807648 亚马逊:http:\/\/www.amazon.cn\/%E4%B8%8D%E8%B4%9F%E5%A6%82%E6%9D%A5%E4%B8%8D%E8%B4%9F%E5%8D%BF-%E5%85%AD%E4%B8%96%E8%BE%BE%E8%B5%96%E4%BB%93%E5%A4%AE%E5%98%89%E6%8E%AA%E7%9A%84%E8%AF%97%E4%B8%8E%E6%83%85-%E5%A7%9A%E6%95%8F\/dp\/B003GDK8PU",
